# Dukko intentionally has no git submodules.
#
# Plan 02 replaced the four template-derived submodules (JUCE, cmake-includes,
# melatonin_inspector, clap-juce-extensions) with CPM-fetched dependencies
# pinned in CMakeLists.txt. Reproducible builds, no submodule init dance.
#
# This file is kept (empty) so cloning Dukko does not produce confusing
# "no .gitmodules" warnings from tools that expect it on a JUCE-flavored repo.
